fields.name: issueSymbolIdentifier
fields.description: Assigned by the NASDAQ listing market and ACT Symbol for Other Exchange Listed (NMS stocks), or by FINRA (OTCE securities). Suffix is separated from root symbol with a special character

fields.name: issueName
fields.description: Company name associated with the Symbol

fields.name: marketParticipantName
fields.description: Company name of the ATS/OTC or or De Minimis Firm

fields.name: tierIdentifier
fields.description: T1 - Securities included in the S&P 500, Russell 1000 and selected exchange-traded products; T2 - All other NMS stocks; OTC - Over-the-Counter equity securities

fields.name: tierDescription
fields.description: NMS Tier 1 - Securities included in the S&P 500, Russell 1000 and selected exchange-traded products; NMS Tier 2 - All other NMS stocks; OTCE - Over-the-Counter equity securities

fields.name: totalWeeklyTradeCount
fields.description: Aggregate weekly total number of trades reported by each ATS for the Symbol

fields.name: totalWeeklyShareQuantity
fields.description: Aggregate weekly total number of shares reported by each ATS for the Symbol

fields.name: summaryTypeCode
fields.description: Report Type Identifier ( OTC_ W_FIRM: OTC Weekly Firm, OTC_ W_SMBL: OTC Weekly Symbol, OTC_ W_SMBL_FIRM: OTC Weekly Symbol Firm, OTC_ W_VOL_STATS: OTC Volume Statistics, ATS_ W_Firm: ATS Weekly Firm, ATS_ W_SMBL: ATS Weekly Symbol, ATS_ W_SMBL_FIRM: ATS Weekly Symbol Firm, ATS_ W_VOL_STATS: ATS Volume Statistics)

fields.name: weekStartDate
fields.description: Partition Key - the first business day of the week (Monday)

fields.name: lastUpdateDate
fields.description: Most recent date on which total trades is updated based on data received from each ATS/OTC

fields.name: initialPublishedDate
fields.description: The initial publish date is the first Monday or next business day after the reporting delay based on NMS Tier 1 (two week delay), NMS Tier 2 (four week delay) and OTC securities (four week delay)

fields.name: lastReportedDate
fields.description: This date represents the last time a firm sent an update to any underlying data that contributes to the aggregate count
